<script type="text/javascript">
	function updatePopUpTitle() {
		var lnk = document.getElementsByTagName('a');
		var text = 'This link opens in a new window.';

		for (var i = 0; i < lnk.length; i++) {
			if (typeof lnk[i].href == 'string' && lnk[i].href.match(/(javascript:)?[^\s()]*pop\S*\(/gi) && lnk[i].title.indexOf(text) == -1) {
				if (lnk[i].title.length > 0) {
					lnk[i].title = lnk[i].title + ' (' + text + ')';
				}
				else {
					lnk[i].title = lnk[i].title + text;
				}
			}
		}
	}

<script type="text/javascript">
	var showDropdown = false;

	function handleDDLEnter(e) {

		if (e.keyCode == 13) {
			ShowDropdown('settingsDd', true);
		}
	}

	function ShowDropdown(id, flag) {
		showDropdown = true;
		isRTL = (document.getElementById("dir-rtl") != null) ? true : false;
		var _el = document.getElementById(id);
		if (_el.style.display == "" || _el.style.display == "none") {
			if (_el.parentElement.tagName != "BODY") {
				document.body.appendChild(_el);
			}
			var _target = document.getElementById("settingscontainer");
			var _top = findPosY(_target);//_target.offsetTop;
			var _height = _target.offsetHeight;
			var _width = _target.offsetWidth;
			_el.style.visibility = "hidden";
			_el.style.display = "block";
			var _left = findPositionX(_target);
			var _ddlWidth = _el.offsetWidth;
			_el.style.zIndex = '99999';
			_el.style.top = ((_top + _height)) + "px";
			_el.style.left = (isRTL) ? _left + "px" : (_left - (_ddlWidth - _width)) + "px";
			_el.style.visibility = "visible";
			if (flag) {
				_el.getElementsByTagName('li')[0].getElementsByTagName('a')[0].focus();
			}
            // add aria attributes 
			document.getElementById('optionsbtn').setAttribute('aria-expanded', true);
			_el.setAttribute('aria-expanded', true);
			_el.setAttribute('aria-hidden', false);
			//_el.focus();
		}
	}

	function HideDropdown(id, focus) {

		//var _target = document.getElementById("settingscontainer");
		var _el = document.getElementById(id);
		//_target.appendChild(_el);
		showDropdown = false;
		setTimeout(function () {
			if (!showDropdown) {
			    _el.style.display = "none";
			    if (focus) {
			        document.getElementById("settingscontainer").getElementsByTagName('a')[0].focus();
			    }
			}
		}, 150); // delay the hide so links are still clickable
	    // add aria attributes 
		document.getElementById('optionsbtn').setAttribute('aria-expanded', false);
		_el.setAttribute('aria-expanded', false);
		_el.setAttribute('aria-hidden', true);
	}

	function ShowHideDropdown(id) {
	    var _el = document.getElementById(id);
	    if (_el.style.display == "" || _el.style.display == "none") {
	        ShowDropdown(id, false);
	    } else {
	        HideDropdown(id, true);
	    }
	}

	function showDDLPopup(el) {
		showDropdown = true;

		if (el != null) {
			var elArray = el.getElementsByTagName('a');
			if (elArray != null && elArray.length > 0) {
				for (var i = 0; i < elArray.length - 1; i++) {
					elArray[i].blur();
				}
			}
		}
	}

	function HandleButtonKey(ev) {
	    if (showDropdown) {
	        if (window.event) {
	            ev = window.event;
	            key = ev.keyCode;
	        } else {
	            key = ev.which;
	        }

	        ev.preventDefault ? ev.preventDefault() : ev.returnValue = false;

	        switch (key) {
	            case 27:
	                {
	                    HideDropdown('settingsDd', true);
	                    break;
	                }
	            case 40:
	                {
	                    var dd = document.getElementById('settingsDd').getElementsByTagName('li')[0].getElementsByTagName('a')[0].focus();
	                    break;
	                }
	        }
	    }
	}

	function handleDDLKey(ev) {
		//var isShift;
		if (window.event) {
			key = window.event.keyCode;
			//isShift = window.event.shiftKey ? true : false;
			ev = window.event;

		} else {
			key = ev.which;
			//isShift = ev.shiftKey ? true : false;
		}

		if (key != 13) {
		    ev.preventDefault ? ev.preventDefault() : ev.returnValue = false;

		    switch (key) {
		        case 9:
		            {
		                ShowHideDropdown('settingsDd');
		                break;
		            }
		        case 27:
		            {
		                HideDropdown('settingsDd', true);
		                break;
		            }
		        case 38:
		            {
		                var isIE8 = (navigator.userAgent.indexOf("MSIE 8.0") > -1) ? true : false;
		                var elTarget = (ev.originalTarget) ? ev.originalTarget : ev.srcElement;
		                var elPrev = isIE8 ? elTarget.parentElement.previousSibling : elTarget.parentElement.previousElementSibling;
		                if (elPrev) elPrev.getElementsByTagName('a')[0].focus();
		                break;
		            }
		        case 40:
		            {
		                var isIE8 = (navigator.userAgent.indexOf("MSIE 8.0") > -1) ? true : false;
		                var elTarget = (ev.originalTarget) ? ev.originalTarget : ev.srcElement;
		                var elNext = isIE8 ? elTarget.parentElement.nextSibling : elTarget.parentElement.nextElementSibling;
		                if (elNext) elNext.getElementsByTagName('a')[0].focus();
		                break;
		            }
		    }
		    //case 9:
		    //    {
		    //        var isIE = (navigator.userAgent.indexOf("MSIE") > -1 || navigator.userAgent.indexOf("Trident") > -1) ? true : false;
		    //        if (!isShift) {
		    //            var elTarget = (ev.originalTarget) ? ev.originalTarget : ev.srcElement;
		    //            var el = isIE ? elTarget.parentElement.nextSibling : elTarget.parentElement.nextElementSibling;
		    //            var elNext = el != null ? isIE ? el.nextSibling : el.nextElementSibling : null;
		    //            if (el == null || elNext == null) {
		    //                HideDropdown('settingsDd');
		    //            }
		    //        } else {
		    //            var elTarget = (ev.originalTarget) ? ev.originalTarget : ev.srcElement;
		    //            var el = isIE ? elTarget.parentElement.previousSibling : elTarget.parentElement.previousElementSibling;
		    //            var elPrev = el != null ? isIE ? el.previousSibling : el.previousElementSibling : null;
		    //            if (el == null || elPrev == null) {
		    //                HideDropdown('settingsDd');
		    //            }
		    //        }
		    //        break;
		    //    }
		}
	}

	function SettingsClicked() {
		// clicking a setting will fire blur first and hide the popup thereby cancelling the click
		// since there's a delay to close, make sure the popup is visible when clicked but then we can close since they clicked already
		ShowDropdown('settingsDd');
		HideDropdown('settingsDd', false);
	}


	function findPosY(obj) {
		var currtop = 0;
		if (obj.offsetParent) {
			while (obj.offsetParent) {
				currtop += obj.offsetTop;
				if (!obj.offsetParent)
					break;
				obj = obj.offsetParent;
			}
		}
		else if (obj.y) {
			currtop += obj.y;
		}
		return currtop;
	}

	function findPositionX(obj) {
		var currleft = 0;
		if (obj.offsetParent) {
			while (obj.offsetParent) {
				currleft += obj.offsetLeft;
				if (!obj.offsetParent)
					break;
				obj = obj.offsetParent;
			}
		}
		else if (obj.x) {
			currleft += obj.x;
		}
		return currleft;
	}
